Things like beauty and rust are just sad excuses for
losing in this poor country with so few resources

957
01:09:28,031 --> 01:09:36,031
"No excuse; if anyone has any information regarding
these lost items please step forward; 
accompanied by the culprit (dog) and prepared to be scolded."

