1045
01:16:01,736 --> 01:16:02,322
Peke.

1046
01:17:25,298 --> 01:17:26,298
Peke.

1047
01:17:26,931 --> 01:17:28,103
Peke.

1048
01:17:30,626 --> 01:17:31,236
Peke.

1049
01:17:32,821 --> 01:17:35,009
I'm sorry

